OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with rain
OL,6,Fclearing later. This afternoon will
OL,7,Fsee some bright or sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers. Showers will be
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy with a chance of
OL,10,Fthunder. Warmer than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be partly
OL,13,Fcloudy with scattered showers, heavy
OL,14,Fat first. Then the rest of the night
OL,15,Fwill see variable amounts of cloud and
OL,16,Fsome showery rain.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,19,Fthrough the day and a scattering of
OL,20,Fshowers. Becoming drier through the
OL,21,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
